title: Alexei Navalny: Poisoned Putin critic 'will return to Russia'
title_page: Alexei Navalny: Poisoned Putin critic 'will return to Russia' - BBC News
maintext: Mr Putin has actually never called Mr Navalny by his name, trying to make it look like this politician is unknown and insignificant. They aim to persuade everyone - in Russia and abroad - that the Kremlin is not paying any attention at all to Mr Navalny's activity, which is obviously far from reality.
